<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Some of you have reached out asking me to review your assignment before you turn it in. Office hours is a great time to do that. If you won&rsquo;t be able to attend office hours in real time but would like your assignment reviewed please let me know and I will do so during office hours and send you the recording.&nbsp;</span></p>
